about.summary: sphinxcontrib-qthelp is a sphinx extension which outputs QtHelp document

name: sphinxcontrib-qthelp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.2" %}

package:
  name: sphinxcontrib-qthelp
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/s/sphinxcontrib-qthelp/sphinxcontrib-qthelp-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 79465ce11ae5694ff165becda529a600c754f4bc459778778c7017374d4d406f

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.5
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  requires:
    # This is a circular dependency b/c sphinx depends on this package now :-/
    - sphinx >=2
  imports:
    - sphinxcontrib
    - sphinxcontrib.qthelp

about:
  home: http://sphinx-doc.org/
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: sphinxcontrib-qthelp is a sphinx extension which outputs QtHelp document

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
